caption.title: UV-inactivated DENV does not regulate AGPAT1 expression.
caption.p: Aag2 cells were infected with an MOI of 5 of DENV (DENV-WT), UV-inactivated DENV (DENV-UV) or mock. Cells were analyzed at 24 and 48 hours post-infection (hpi). (A) DENV gRNA copies. Bars show geometric means ± 95% C.I. (B) AGPAT1 expression relative to Actin level. Bars show arithmetic means ± s.e.m. (A-B) Each point represents an independent well. ***, p-value < 0.001 as determined by unpaired t-test.
